/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the cityscape. The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, flanked by buildings on either side. Power lines crisscross above, forming a complex web against the backdrop of the clear blue sky. The sun shines brightly in the top right corner of the image, casting a warm glow over the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, adding a sense of depth and perspective to the view.
